title: Detox Your Mind Through Meditation - Hinsdale Library
author: Meghan Hall
description: The world can be a stressful place and there are many factors that can have a negative impact on our daily lives. Join Zelma Chamberlain, M. Ed. and long time meditator, to learn how to detoxify the mind.
